          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='9'>East leads with ₹22,91,515 net revenue (26.5% of total), driven by the Electronics category. Reason: East has the highest concentration of high‑ticket Electronics orders (UltraBook, SmartPhone). Action: replicate East’s Electronics bundling strategy in North — currently ₹1,16,340 behind — to lift North’s share.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
